    "The findings presented in Table 3 indicate that KTO and IPO outperform SFT by 17.5%, whereas KTO, based on a pre-trained model, outperforms SFT by 9.5% (See Table 9 in Appendix B).",
    "This underscores the high effectiveness of an instruction-tuned model, particularly in terms of truthfulness.",
    "Additionally, it is observed that KTO surpasses other methods in MT-Bench (See Table 4).",
    "SFT based on instruction tuning is enough.",
